# Plan
Plan before building. Do NOT implement.
Observe → Orient → Decide → Act.
Read request. Explore codebase. Generate multiple approaches. Write doc/plans/<PLANNAME>.md.
Plan contains: Goal, Constraints, Options (pros/cons), Chosen approach, Steps, Edge cases, Open questions, Fitness functions.
Surface contradictions and ambiguities. Flag incoherence. Tell user when ready. Implement on "Go."
